text: Philippe Cuelenaere (born 2 September 1971) is a Belgian rower. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Belgium Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Royal Club Nautique de Gand rowers
